### P5: Same Tree (LC #100)
**Problem:** Check if two binary trees are identical (same structure and values).

def isSameTree(p, q):
    if not p and not q:    # both null → same
        return True
    if not p or not q:     # one null, one not → different
        return False
    if p.val != q.val:     # values differ
        return False
    return isSameTree(p.left, q.left) and isSameTree(p.right, q.right)
```
===================================================================
**Key cases to handle:**
1. Both null → True
2. One null → False
3. Values differ → False
4. Recurse on children

**Time:** O(n) | **Space:** O(h)

