### P6: Invert Binary Tree (LC #226)

**Problem:** Mirror the binary tree (swap left and right at every node).

```
Before:        After:
    4              4
   / \            / \
  2   7    →    7   2
 / \ / \       / \ / \
1  3 6  9     9  6 3  1
```

```python
def invertTree(root):
    if not root:
        return None
    root.left, root.right = invertTree(root.right), invertTree(root.left)
    return root
```

**Time:** O(n) | **Space:** O(h)

